16#include <config.h>
17
18#include <stdbool.h>
19
20#include <isc/magic.h>
21#include <isc/mem.h>
22#include <isc/types.h>
23#include <isc/util.h>
24#include <isc/refcount.h>
25
26#include <dns/fixedname.h>
27#include <dns/name.h>
28#include <dns/order.h>
29#include <dns/rdataset.h>
30#include <dns/types.h>
31
32typedef struct dns_order_ent dns_order_ent_t;
33struct dns_order_ent {
34 dns_fixedname_t name;
35 dns_rdataclass_t rdclass;
36 dns_rdatatype_t rdtype;
37 unsigned int mode;
38 ISC_LINK(dns_order_ent_t) link;
39};
40
41struct dns_order {
42 unsigned int magic;
43 isc_refcount_t references;
44 ISC_LIST(dns_order_ent_t) ents;
45 isc_mem_t *mctx;
46};
47
48#define DNS_ORDER_MAGIC ISC_MAGIC('O','r','d','r')
49#define DNS_ORDER_VALID(order) ISC_MAGIC_VALID(order, DNS_ORDER_MAGIC)
50
51isc_result_t
52dns_order_create(isc_mem_t *mctx, dns_order_t **orderp) {
53 dns_order_t *order;
54
55 REQUIRE(orderp != NULL && *orderp == NULL);
56
57 order = isc_mem_get(mctx, sizeof(*order));
58 if (order == NULL)
59 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
60
61 ISC_LIST_INIT(order->ents);
62
63 /* Implicit attach. */
64 isc_refcount_init(&order->references, 1);
65
66 order->mctx = NULL;
67 isc_mem_attach(mctx, &order->mctx);
68 order->magic = DNS_ORDER_MAGIC;
69 *orderp = order;
70 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
71}
72
73isc_result_t
74dns_order_add(dns_order_t *order, const dns_name_t *name,
75 dns_rdatatype_t rdtype, dns_rdataclass_t rdclass,
76 unsigned int mode)
77{
78 dns_order_ent_t *ent;
79
80 REQUIRE(DNS_ORDER_VALID(order));
81 REQUIRE(mode == DNS_RDATASETATTR_RANDOMIZE ||
82 mode == DNS_RDATASETATTR_FIXEDORDER ||
83 mode == DNS_RDATASETATTR_CYCLIC);
84
85 ent = isc_mem_get(order->mctx, sizeof(*ent));
86 if (ent == NULL)
87 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
88
89 dns_fixedname_init(&ent->name);
90 RUNTIME_CHECK(dns_name_copy(name, dns_fixedname_name(&ent->name), NULL)
91 == ISC_R_SUCCESS);
92 ent->rdtype = rdtype;
93 ent->rdclass = rdclass;
94 ent->mode = mode;
95 ISC_LINK_INIT(ent, link);
96 ISC_LIST_INITANDAPPEND(order->ents, ent, link);
97 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
98}
99
100static inline bool
101match(const dns_name_t *name1, const dns_name_t *name2) {
102
103 if (dns_name_iswildcard(name2))
104 return(dns_name_matcheswildcard(name1, name2));
105 return (dns_name_equal(name1, name2));
106}
107
108unsigned int
109dns_order_find(dns_order_t *order, const dns_name_t *name,
110 dns_rdatatype_t rdtype, dns_rdataclass_t rdclass)
111{
112 dns_order_ent_t *ent;
113 REQUIRE(DNS_ORDER_VALID(order));
114
115 for (ent = ISC_LIST_HEAD(order->ents);
116 ent != NULL;
117 ent = ISC_LIST_NEXT(ent, link)) {
118 if (ent->rdtype != rdtype && ent->rdtype != dns_rdatatype_any)
119 continue;
120 if (ent->rdclass != rdclass &&
121 ent->rdclass != dns_rdataclass_any)
122 continue;
123 if (match(name, dns_fixedname_name(&ent->name)))
124 return (ent->mode);
125 }
126 return (DNS_RDATASETATTR_NONE);
127}
128
129void
130dns_order_attach(dns_order_t *source, dns_order_t **target) {
131 REQUIRE(DNS_ORDER_VALID(source));
132 REQUIRE(target != NULL && *target == NULL);
133 isc_refcount_increment(&source->references);
134 *target = source;
135}
136
137void
138dns_order_detach(dns_order_t **orderp) {
139 REQUIRE(orderp != NULL && DNS_ORDER_VALID(*orderp));
140 dns_order_t *order;
141 order = *orderp;
142 *orderp = NULL;
143
144 if (isc_refcount_decrement(&order->references) == 1) {
145 isc_refcount_destroy(&order->references);
146 order->magic = 0;
147 dns_order_ent_t *ent;
148 while ((ent = ISC_LIST_HEAD(order->ents)) != NULL) {
149 ISC_LIST_UNLINK(order->ents, ent, link);
150 isc_mem_put(order->mctx, ent, sizeof(*ent));
151 }
152 isc_mem_putanddetach(&order->mctx, order, sizeof(*order));
153 }
